{
  "stem": "18281.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 406.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I wanted to go home as fast as possible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did not, no, no, really no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe that the Germans pulled back from that area and very fast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That, that also accounts for the call of the underground that wanted me to come and help fight the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was nobody to fight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would say they pulled back very fast from that area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You only saw them parade in the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the people that I dealt with, I didn't see them again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I got out of there fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I, I first moved into my uncle's house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had a few-- I had given him all, all my belongings before I left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a, a little bit of money left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister came out of the convent school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandmother still lived in the old place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She never had a day's problems with the, with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to support them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had to find a job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's what I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I started selling labels.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And first of all, I started selling anything you could find.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember blouses and rubber balls and watches and whatever you could find.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everything was at a premium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everything was in short supply.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when somebody gave you a sample of something, you went to somebody else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You want to buy this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You went back to the first guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the goods were gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's that's how you try to earn a living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I worked-- Did you go back to school?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's funny.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Paul asked me-- my grandson asked me, how come you didn't go back to school?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to earn a living.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
